description: The very best of UB40. Includes the big hits One in ten, Food for thought, Rat in mi kitchen, If it happens again and Breakfast in bed but also excellent cover versions of Red red wine, I got you babe, I'll be your baby tonight, Kingston Town and (I can't help) Falling in love with you.
